## 5. Sesame Care Reference (UX patterns to clone)

sesamecare.com key UX patterns for the services browser:
- Dark-on-white card grid in production; adapt to dark theme for this demo
- Each card: provider photo placeholder (avatar initials circle), name, specialty, star rating, price chip, "Book" CTA button
- Card layout: 3-col on desktop, 1-col on mobile (CSS grid: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)))
- Price displayed as "$XX / visit" in a colored chip (use --mustard background)
- Rating displayed as filled stars + numeric (e.g. "4.9 (48 reviews)")
- Header: site name + role badge + logout; minimal, no sidebar
- The booking slot picker: a compact date/time grid or segmented list of available times

